PL_SCMSTO_INF.@EndUserText.label: Purchase Order Schedule Lines Interface
PL_SCMSTO_INF.@DataWarehouse.tableFunction.script:
/**
    * return select "Column1","Column2" from "table";
*/
VAR_OUT = 
SELECT 
"EBELN", --as "PO Number",
"EBELP",--as "PO Item",
"ETENR",-- as "PO Schedule Line",
"BSART",--as "Purchasing Doc. Type",
"MATNR",--as "Material",
"WERKS",--as "Plant",
"RESWK",--as "Supplying plant",
"AEDAT", --as "Created On",
"EINDT",--as "Requested Del Date",
"DOCUMENT_DATE",--as "Document Date",
"SCHEDULED_QUANTITY",--as "Order Qty",
"ZK_GKMNG", -- as "Delivered Quantity",
"ZK_WAMNG",-- as "Shipped Quatity",
"EFFWR",-- as "Order Value",
"BSGRU",-- as "Order for Reason",
"ELIKZ", --as "Delivery Completed",
"LOEKZ", --as "Deletion Indicator",
"ZZWEMNG_EKET",--as "Goods Received Qty",
"BEDNR",-- as " Cancel Reason",
ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY "EBELN") AS "RCOUNT",
"WADAT", -- as "Goods Issue Date"
"VKORG", -- as "Sales Organization"
TO_TIMESTAMP("TIME_STAMP") AS "TIME_STAMP",-- as "Time Stamp"
"ALLOC_QTY" -- as Allocated Undelivered Qty
FROM "HL_SCM_PO_SCHDLN_SCL"
;

RETURN :VAR_OUT;
